76561198031306289,Recommended,287980,11795999,"Posted: 20 August, 2014",all,KomradZX,"In simulation games, people commonly think that the more complex you make the game, the more realistic it becomes. That notion couldn't be more wrong with Mini Metro. With the few simple set of rules and design, Dinosaur Polo Club has created a true masterpiece. Ever since I played my very first Sim City game when I was 5 I have always dreamed of a game exactly like this. Sure there have been plenty of other transportation simulators made, but the learning curb is almost always far too steep for all but the very, very few hardcore gamers out there.Mini Metro really shows just how good a simple idea can become such a rich and fullfilling game. There are very few games like this that can attract people who would have never tried any simulation game because of the mind-boggling complexity. Mini Metro is a perfect example of how casual gamers can suddenly find themselves obsessed like the hardcore gamer without hardcore learning curb associated with nearly every simulation game out there. This game is perfect for ANYONE and EVERYONE!"
