76561197997389079,Recommended,287980,28653286,"Posted: 25 December, 2016",all,ActualScreenshot,"Really well designed, really well made, addictive game. Hours just disappear when you play this.The controls are solid and intuitive so you don't need a tutorial. You just get going straight away. The map starts off by easing you in gently and it's really satisfying watching your abstract passengers get from A to B. Then as more stations automatically come online the complexity begins to build until you're in charge of a sprawling tube map. The layout is minimalist and beautiful and the game flows from start to finish. There are so many nice touches like the smooth ambient sounds that portray a clean efficient system, which is what you're always striving to make. Everything just whispers quality. I love this game."
